Package: cuci
Title: Clean and Unify Collected Information
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yusman", "Kamaleri", , "ybkamaleri@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a pipeline for matching, recoding, type-coercing, and
    validating dataset columns based on a declarative YAML variable map.
    Supports three-layer column matching (exact, fuzzy, keyword), safe type
    conversion with warnings, value-label validation, recode tables, and
    structured audit logging.
URL: https://folkehelsestats.github.io/cuci/, https://github.com/folkehelsestats/cuci
